{"tid":40192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[GAY]普京訪日 安倍同到溫泉浴「肉帛相見」","createTime":"2016-12-15T05:01:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T11:12:42.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"850ea525b86e345186c542d7fba0a279f0351b14","tid":40192,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:01:54.000Z","msg":"【晴報專訊】俄羅斯總統普京今明兩日訪問日本，在日本首相安倍晉三家鄉山口縣進行「溫泉外交」，安倍希望拉近二人關係，解決北方四島領土主權問題。 <br />\n<br />\n普京十年來首次正式訪日，獲安倍邀請在其家鄉山口縣長門市的溫泉旅館住宿一晚，或會同到溫泉浸浴「肉帛相見」，通過「溫泉外交」解決兩國長期以來的北方四島領土問題。兩人明日往東京，舉行經濟合作會談，將簽署多份協議。 <br />\n<br />\n奧巴馬阻不了 日美現分歧 <br />\n<br />\n普京在領土問題立場強硬，他訪日前接受日媒訪問，指日方要求歸還北方四島，超出兩國在1956年簽訂共同宣言的範疇，俄方認為主權爭議不存在，暗示要日方讓步才會簽署和平友好條約。他亦指責日本跟隨西方制裁俄國阻礙關係發展，但願意與日方商討在北方四島開展經濟合作，前提是必須在俄國領土內進行。俄國官員亦明言，雙方難透過一次峰會解決困擾雙方71年的領土問題。 <br />\n<br />\n安倍近年積極與普京交好，圖打破只依賴美國，拉攏俄國牽制中國。對普京而言，日本之行同擁有巨大潛在利益，他可藉此吸引日商投資，突破西方經濟制裁，同時減少經濟上對中國依賴。 <br />\n<br />\n是次日俄首腦會議被視為日美分歧跡象，美國總統奧巴馬曾要求日方勿在東京舉行首腦會談，認為此舉影響美國和西方制裁俄羅斯的措施。"},{"pid":"0a2169388245c19873ed09cbe83ad2b21cda19db","tid":40192,"uid":516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:03:29.000Z","msg":"奧巴馬跟本垃圾黎"},{"pid":"f8e8456060ef330e785ad3f131f0fad50809c508","tid":40192,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:05:52.000Z","msg":"拉近兩人關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c635fb4c93fe1da1ed5752d5e1d7a0b6b79889a","tid":40192,"uid":16914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:12:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>奧巴馬跟本垃圾黎</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d6988b533e58bd719fc877f562643a43105d904a","tid":40192,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:15:52.000Z","msg":"諗起民王"},{"pid":"d47b71fd87583b5e16d7255699a2c8606bd05e0b","tid":40192,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T08:01:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f87cec32bfe89f843fe015e5a2b3443a59b956d9","tid":40192,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T08:39:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拉近兩人關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊個係零仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e68bdbc1a65578fa1c07fe660b004cf8526325e8","tid":40192,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T08:48:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>拉近兩人關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊個係零仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔洗問都知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"256f18ad7bb2b15400f2506a0392759a07810a30","tid":40192,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T11:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}